AmigaKickstart Plymouth Theme
Version 1.0 - 02/03/23


What:
A free animated Amiga Kickstart startup, shutdown, and reboot theme to add some retro magic to your Linux installation.



Installation:


1. Copy the AmigaKickstart folder to your Plymouth themes folder located here:

/usr/share/plymouth/themes/


2. Verify Plymouth can see the theme via the termianl with this command:

plymouth-set-default-theme -l

You should see AmigaKickstart listed among your themes.


3. Make AmigaKickstart the default theme:

sudo plymouth-set-default-theme -R AmigaKickstart


Done!



Issues:

Let me know if you have any issues.


Enjoy!
